{"tid":225551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加拿大軍駐紮拉脫維亞 拉脫維亞將部署更多美軍基地和北約基地","createTime":"2017-05-02T00:03:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-02T21:28:00.000Z","uid":100986,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dc48278c905cd0899e53113b606976dd25e06708","tid":225551,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T00:03:52.000Z","msg":"加拿大軍駐紮拉脫維亞 拉脫維亞將部署更多美軍基地和北約基地<br />\n憂心平民遭網絡攻擊 加拿大、北約正研究對策<br />\n<br />\n隨著加拿大領導的北約（NATO）駐拉脫維亞（Latvia）部隊，將在今夏調集到位，目前加拿大與北約正在權衡如何應對潛在重大網絡攻擊的問題。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大和北約對平民百姓的網絡遭受重大攻擊的憂心，超過了軍隊基礎設施可能受到的網絡攻擊。因為2007年同樣是波羅的海國家之一的愛沙尼亞，在遭到網絡攻擊之後，政府機構與銀行業務一度癱瘓。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大國防總參謀長數週前表示，網絡戰士將被部署在駐拉脫維亞軍隊之列。但是他們能夠在多大程度上應對來自俄羅斯的網絡和信息戰威脅，仍是一個有待討論的問題。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大軍隊的網絡聯合部隊司令盧瑟福（Paul Rutherford）對CBC表示，北約或加拿大無意發起針對黑客等的網絡攻擊，而會採取一種強大、防禦性的網絡安全措施。<br />\n<br />\n防禦專家稱，從軍事和政治角度來看，制定正確的規則至關重要。<br />\n<br />\n責任編輯：文風<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/17/3/22/n8955196.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F17%2F3%2F22%2Fn8955196.htm&d=Z0jJ2Ci5UPqU8nDHOGo4vP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=52737c88\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/17/3/22/n8955196.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Canada military signs agreement with Latvia for upcoming NATO deployment</strong><br />\nApril 18, 2017<br />\n<img src=\"http://wpmedia.ottawacitizen.com/2017/04/13058305.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwpmedia.ottawacitizen.com%2F2017%2F04%2F13058305.jpg&h=428647cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nThis summer Canada will lead a multinational NATO battlegroup in Latvia as part of what the military has called the alliance&rsquo;s enhanced Forward Presence (eFP) in Central and Eastern Europe. A technical arrangement was signed Tuesday by Brigadier-General Bruce Ploughman, Chief of Staff Readiness Canadian Joint Operations Command, and Brigadier-General Ivo Mogilnijs, Chief of Staff of the Joint Headquarters of the Latvian National Armed Forces during a ceremony in Riga, Latvia.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ottawacitizen.com/news/national/defence-watch/canada-military-signs-agreement-with-latvia-for-upcoming-nato-deployment\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fottawacitizen.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fdefence-watch%2Fcanada-military-signs-agreement-with-latvia-for-upcoming-nato-deployment&d=Z0jJ2Ci5UPqU8nDHOGo4vP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=ec29fd8d\" target=\"_blank\">http://ottawacitizen.com/news/national/defence-watch/canada-military-signs-agreement-with-latvia-for-upcoming-nato-deployment</a>"},{"pid":"37950491040958e353bb0ba6939a39f9180ddf88","tid":225551,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T00:06:37.000Z","msg":"美軍同加軍得加加埋埋都唔夠一千人, 點夠俄佬打. 雖然三小國一樣係正牌NATO成員國<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739e9d4a3b8bfe7a97a9ffb1fb4841cbdbac6e6c","tid":225551,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T00:07:45.000Z","msg":"美軍同加軍得加加埋埋都唔夠一千人, 點夠俄佬打(萬一俄佬好似北韓咁發左癲咁). 雖然三小國一樣都係正牌NATO成員國<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c93ef283d36061bca2cb9a3510a0c5b6d40366e","tid":225551,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T00:08:38.000Z","msg":"奧巴馬做法:<br />\n美國兩線作戰, 美國o係西線和歐洲依靠北約(北約成員國愛沙尼亞、拉脫維亞、立陶宛、波蘭、羅馬尼亞)圍堵俄羅斯, 美國o係東線和亞洲獨自(美日軍事同盟同美韓軍事同盟, 日本、南韓同越南, 亞洲再平衡同TPP)圍堵中國和施壓北韓<br />\n<br />\nTrump做法:<br />\n彈性地聯俄制中或彈性地聯中制俄, 先(依靠北約)打擊俄羅斯"},{"pid":"dfee1335b37029cd4839abc0dd2f7ca7bf5ca191","tid":225551,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T00:12:42.000Z","msg":"美國同北約下一輪擴員名單:<br />\n芬蘭同瑞典(芬蘭同瑞典肯唔肯入埋北約就另一回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 芬蘭和瑞典兩國只入歐盟., 兩國應該一早入埋北約. 話曬芬蘭自1917年12月脫離帝俄獨立, 獨立初期既芬蘭、獨立初期既愛沙尼亞、獨立初期既拉脫維亞同德國聯手合作擊退俄羅斯紅色赤衛軍, 芬蘭同俄佬前身蘇聯史魔都打過Talvisota和繼續戰爭, 芬蘭和俄佬係世仇."},{"pid":"7dffcff8abe6b77e9643f64d6ab95e844dc44e6f","tid":225551,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T01:05:09.000Z","msg":"愛沙尼亞、拉脫維亞和立陶宛:<br />\n蘇聯和 &ldquo;俄國人&rdquo; 史太林永遠比納粹德國(和SS黨衛軍)更壞更殘暴.<br />\n<br />\nEstonian WW2 poster comp (Axis)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.fjcdn.com/pictures/Estonian+ww2+poster+comp+axis+translation+for+the+posters+are_da93e3_5426614.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.fjcdn.com%2Fpictures%2FEstonian%2Bww2%2Bposter%2Bcomp%2Baxis%2Btranslation%2Bfor%2Bthe%2Bposters%2Bare_da93e3_5426614.jpg&h=8264f285&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.fjcdn.com/pictures/Estonian_11cbee_5426614.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.fjcdn.com%2Fpictures%2FEstonian_11cbee_5426614.jpg&h=30cfcfe2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.fjcdn.com/pictures/Estonian_2e944a_5426614.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.fjcdn.com%2Fpictures%2FEstonian_2e944a_5426614.jpg&h=708f8a8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.fjcdn.com/pictures/Estonian_95831f_5426614.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.fjcdn.com%2Fpictures%2FEstonian_95831f_5426614.jpg&h=c4c694ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.fjcdn.com/pictures/Estonian_4c46da_5426614.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.fjcdn.com%2Fpictures%2FEstonian_4c46da_5426614.jpg&h=7a7915ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.fjcdn.com/pictures/Estonian_942d6a_5426614.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.fjcdn.com%2Fpictures%2FEstonian_942d6a_5426614.jpg&h=74df16fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.fjcdn.com/pictures/Estonian_cbcbd3_5426614.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.fjcdn.com%2Fpictures%2FEstonian_cbcbd3_5426614.jpg&h=0df7bdb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.fjcdn.com/pictures/Estonian_2a82db_5426614.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.fjcdn.com%2Fpictures%2FEstonian_2a82db_5426614.jpg&h=84231572&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.fjcdn.com/pictures/Estonian_32c7bb_5426614.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.fjcdn.com%2Fpictures%2FEstonian_32c7bb_5426614.jpg&h=d61d4af4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.fjcdn.com/pictures/Estonian_f136e7_5426614.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.fjcdn.com%2Fpictures%2FEstonian_f136e7_5426614.jpg&h=6818d7fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.funnyjunk.com/Estonian+ww2+poster+comp+axis/funny-pictures/5427058/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.funnyjunk.com%2FEstonian%2Bww2%2Bposter%2Bcomp%2Baxis%2Ffunny-pictures%2F5427058%2F&d=Z0jJ2Ci5UPqU8nDHOGo4vP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=a6c511d8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.funnyjunk.com/Estonian+ww2+poster+comp+axis/funny-pictures/5427058/</a>"},{"pid":"581a6a9149761157b4d041b1f4e1e9e7896e501c","tid":225551,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T02:16:22.000Z","msg":"Latvia Waffen-SS <br />\n<img src=\"https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/originals/5b/b2/dd/5bb2dd0f42d8fc237e4682dc181fb0d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F5b%2Fb2%2Fdd%2F5bb2dd0f42d8fc237e4682dc181fb0d8.jpg&h=674a509b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3567462860fcd9846cfce5f771245716ee2f5a1e","tid":225551,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T03:18:29.000Z","msg":"[觀察]迎接特朗普國防新時代(上)：中東東歐大局不變<br />\n<strong>2016年11月25日</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.theepochtimes.com/n3/eet-content/uploads/2016/11/17/GettyImages-622165118-crop.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.theepochtimes.com%2Fn3%2Feet-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F11%2F17%2FGettyImages-622165118-crop.jpg&h=83229560&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>特朗普的取態將影響世界勢力平衡。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://d3i6fh83elv35t.cloudfront.net/newshour/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/RTSSHZ0-1024x638.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fd3i6fh83elv35t.cloudfront.net%2Fnewshour%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F11%2FRTSSHZ0-1024x638.jpg&h=7189b4cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>美國總統奧巴馬將卸任，繼任的特朗普與俄羅斯總統普京的關係備受關注。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ip9vmnzxbIDQ/v0/-1x-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.bwbx.io%2Fimages%2Fusers%2FiqjWHBFdfxIU%2Fip9vmnzxbIDQ%2Fv0%2F-1x-1.jpg&h=9e6f0665&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>Russia Vows Retaliation After Obama Expels Diplomats for Hacking</strong><br />\nJanuary 4, 2017, 8:39 pm<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bloombergquint.com/technology/2016/12/29/u-s-hits-russian-officials-with-sanctions-over-election-hacks\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloombergquint.com%2Ftechnology%2F2016%2F12%2F29%2Fu-s-hits-russian-officials-with-sanctions-over-election-hacks&d=Z0jJ2Ci5UPqU8nDHOGo4vP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=9d754361\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bloombergquint.com/technology/2016/12/29/u-s-hits-russian-officials-with-sanctions-over-election-hacks</a><br />\n<br />\n新聞 , [觀察]迎接特朗普國防新時代(上)：中東東歐大局不變      <br />\n <br />\n[觀察]國際關係學者／分析員之所以對特朗普上台憂心忡忡，乃源自其立場猶如瘋子駕車：他指出美國在世界各地駐軍及軍事干預的成本與利益不成比例，建議大規模撤出美軍走向孤立主義、甚至主動提出將對抗ISIS責任交予普京。然而如今特朗普真的成為了美國總統，那我們亦好應探討一下，他將會引領這個世界前往哪裡去。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://archive.am730.com.hk/article-339052\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Farchive.am730.com.hk%2Farticle-339052&d=Z0jJ2Ci5UPqU8nDHOGo4vP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%